subject: Attn: Sir/Madam
body:
Attn: Sir/Madam
This is  to inform you for the second time that your ATM CARD is out and ready to be sent to your address. You are advised to reply back to me for more details.I wait to hear from you as Soon as possible.
Thanks,
Dr. James David

subject: Re: Attn: Sir/Madam
body:
Hello Dr. James David,

Thank you for reaching out to me! I'm thrilled to hear about the ATM card. Could you please provide more details about it? Like, what bank is it associated with and what are the benefits of this card?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Earlene
